metadata.name: Aevum
metadata.description:
Aevum is a state between eternity and temporality and can only be fully grasped using dream logic. It's always beside us, in its changeless state. 

Jono K is an artist, writer and mostly graphical novelist fascinated by mysticism, eclecticism and history. 

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.

2023
4608x6144
Stable Diffusion 2.1 + in-painting.
